annotationA: Probable ribosome biogenesis protein RLP24; Involved in the biogenesis of the 60S ribosomal subunit. Ensures the docking of NOG1 to pre-60S particles (By similarity)
annotationB: LD11307p; RNA binding; S-adenosylmethionine-dependent methyltransferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: rRNA processing; Belongs to the class I-like SAM-binding methyltransferase superfamily. RsmB/NOP family
